skill.name: Orb of Deception
skill.desc: Ahri fires an orb in a line, dealing magic damage to all enemies it passes through on the way out, and true damage one the way back.

skill.name: Galaxy Shield-Blast
skill.desc: Annie blasts a cone of fire dealing magic damage to enemies in front of her, then creates a shield for herself for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Enchanted Crystal Arrow
skill.desc: Ashe fires and arrow toward the farthest enemy, colliding with the first enemy hit, dealing damage and stunning them. The stun lasts longer the farther the arrow travels.

skill.name: Mobilize the Fleet
skill.desc: Aurelion Sol launches fighters, which fly out to random enemies, deal magic damage, and then return. Aurelion Sol launches all ready fighters plus 3 additional when he casts. Fighters prefer to target nearby enemies.

skill.name: Rocket Grab
skill.desc: Blitzcrank pulls the furthest enemy to him, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 2.5 seconds. The next attack after pulling knocks up for 1 second. Allies within range will prioritize attacking Blitzcrank's target.

skill.name: Ace in the Hole
skill.desc: Caitlyn takes aim at the furthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.

skill.name: Rupture
skill.desc: Cho'Gath ruptures a large area, dealing magic damage and knocking up all enemies within.

skill.name: Dreadnova Guillotine
skill.desc:
Darius dunks an enemy, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Darius immediately casts again.
Targets below 50% health take double damage.

skill.name: Chronobreak
skill.desc: Ekko shatters the timeline, freezing all units in time before attacking each enemy with bonus magic damage and applying on-hit effects.

skill.name: E.M.P.
skill.desc: Ezreal fires an electromagnetic pulse at a random enemy that explodes on impact, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and increases the cost of their next spell cast by 40%.

skill.name: Reposte
skill.desc: Fiora enters a defensive stance for a seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy spell effects. As she exits this stance, she ripostes, dealing magic damage and stunning them for a second.

skill.name: Chum the Waters
skill.desc: Fizz throws a lure that attracts a shark, causing it to emerge after a brief delay. It deals magic damage to enemies caught, knocking them back and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Orbital Strike
skill.desc: Gangplank calls down a large orbital strike around his target, dealing magic damage to all enemies in that area for 2 seconds.

skill.name: Smoke Grenade
skill.desc: Graves launches a smoke grenade toward the highest attack speed enemy, which explodes on impact dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and causing their attacks to miss for a second.

skill.name: Bladesurge
skill.desc: Irelia dashes past her target, attacking them for a percentage of her Attack Damage as she passes through. If this kills the target, she casts again immediately at the enemy with the highest mana.

skill.name: Ageless Standard
skill.desc: Jarvan calls down his standard to a nearby location, granting nearby allies Attack Speed for 6 seconds.

skill.name: To the Skies!
skill.desc: Jayce jumps into the air and slams his hammer, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.

skill.name: Whisper
skill.desc: Passive: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals bonus % attack damage.

skill.name: Get Excited!
skill.desc:
Passive: Jinx gets excited as she helps take down enemy units!
After her first takedown, Jinx gains bonus Attack Speed.
After her second takedown, Jinx swaps to her rocket launcher, causing her Basic Attacks to deal bonus magic damage to all enemies in a small area around her target.

skill.name: Missile Rain
skill.desc: Kai'Sa launches missiles towards each nearby enemy that deal 50 magic damage each.

skill.name: Inspire
skill.desc:
At start of combat, Karma bonds to her closest ally.
Karma grants the bonded ally (or a random one if that ally is dead) a health shield for 4 seconds. While the shield holds, the ally receives bonus Attack Speed.

skill.name: Force Pulse
skill.desc: Kassadin releases a wave of energy in front of him, dealing magic damage and disarming all targets.

skill.name: Ascend
skill.desc: Kayle Ascends, causing her attacks to launch waves that deal bonus magic damage until the end of combat.

skill.name: Taste their Fear
skill.desc: Kha'Zix slashes the nearest enemy, dealing magic damage. If the target has no adjacent teammates, this damage is increased.

skill.name: Cyber Barrier
skill.desc: Leona creates a barrier, reducing all incoming damage for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Relentless Persuit
skill.desc: Lucian dashes away from his current target, then Basic Attacks them and fires a second shot which deals magic damage.

skill.name: Massive Polymorph
skill.desc: Lulu polymorphs a number of the nearest enemies, causing them to hop aimlessly, unable to attack or cast. Polymorphed enemies take additional damage from all sources.

skill.name: Lurid Binding
skill.desc: Lux fires a sphere of darkness that passes through enemies, dealing magic damage and stunning them.

skill.name: Energy Shield
skill.desc: Passive: Malphite starts combat with a shield equal to a percent of his maximum health.

skill.name: Chosen One
skill.desc: For 5 seconds, Master Yi gains massively increased movement speed, heals for a percentage of his maximum health each second, and deals bonus true damage with his Basic Attacks.

skill.name: Bullet Time
skill.desc: Miss Fortune channels and fires waves of bullets in a cone for 2.25 seconds, dealing a percentage of enemies' maximum health in magic damage over the duration.

skill.name: Cyclone
skill.desc: Wukong spins, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies. The first time Wukong hits each enemy, he knocks them into the air and stuns them.

skill.name: Indestructible
skill.desc: Mordekaiser gains a shield that absorbs damage. While the shield persists, Mordekaiser deals magic damage per second to all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Pop Blossom
skill.desc: Neeko leaps into the air and slams into the ground, dealing magic damage and stunning all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Buckler Toss
skill.desc: Poppy throws her buckler at the furthest enemy dealing damage. The buckler bounces back to Poppy, shielding her.

skill.name: Grand Entrance
skill.desc: Rakan dashes next to farthest unit within attack range +1 hex then leaps into the air, knocking up and damaging all adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Flamespitter
skill.desc: Rumble torches his enemies, dealing magic damage over 3 seconds, and reducing healing on them by 50% for 5 seconds.

skill.name: Deceive
skill.desc: Shaco teleports and backstabs his target, critically striking for a percentage of his Basic Attack damage.

skill.name: Future's Refuge
skill.desc: Shen creates a zone around himself for a few seconds, granting all narby allies 100% chance to dodge incoming basic attacks. While active, Shen gains Magic Resist.

skill.name: Aria of Perseverance
skill.desc: Sona heals injured allies and cleanses them stuns

skill.name: Wish
skill.desc: Soraka heals all allies.

skill.name: Unleashed Power
skill.desc: Syndra pulls in all orbs on the battlefield and creates 3 new ones, then fires them all at the enemy with the highest health, dealing magic damage per orb.

skill.name: Temporal Passage
skill.desc: Thresh tosses his lantern towards random unit(s) on your bench, pulling them into the current combat and granting them and himself bonus mana. Traits are unaffected.

skill.name: Wild Cards
skill.desc: Twisted Fate throws three cards in a cone that deal magic damage to each enemy they pass through.

skill.name: Lifeform Disintegration Ray
skill.desc: Vel'Koz channels a ray of energy that sweeps across the battlefield over 2 seconds, dealing magic damage per second to enemies hit.

skill.name: Assault and Battery
skill.desc: Vi charges at the furthest enemy, knocking and dealing magic damage to all enemies along the way. When she reaches her target, she deals magic damage and knocks them up.

skill.name: Deadly Plumage
skill.desc: Xayah creates a storm of blades, gaining Attack Speed for a few seconds.

skill.name: Abyssal Bombardment
skill.desc: Xerath transforms, summoning meteors to strike random foes in place of his normal attacks for a seconds. Meteors deal magic damage upon impact and if they kill their target, all adjacent enemies take (% of base damage) 25% magic damage and are stunned for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Three Talon Strike
skill.desc: Xin Zhao quickly strikes his target three times, dealing Basic Attack damage and applying on-hit effects. The third strike deals bonus magic damage and knocks his target up for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Last Breath
skill.desc: Yasuo blinks to the enemy with farthest unit within attack range + 2 hexes and knocks them into the air for 1 second, hits them several times for Basic Attack damage and on-hit effects.

skill.name: Bomb!
skill.desc: Ziggs throws a bomb at an enemy, dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Sleepy Trouble Bubble
skill.desc: Zoe kicks a bubble at the enemy with the highest health, dealing magic damage and stunning them.
